#Use following steps-:

-Create new project
-Enter the name of your Project
-There will the options for which type of program you are going to do, choose one.
-Select Cross GCC as your toolchain
-Enter arm-linux-gnueabihf for cross compiler prefix
-Choose the path to /usr/bin(cross compiler path)
-Write your program
-And finally Run it. YOU will get the Result.
